WEBVTT

00:08.209 --> 00:10.111
Marnie:
I CAN'T BELIEVE
WE'RE TWO HOURS LATE.

00:10.211 --> 00:12.180
IT'S A GIGANTIC
FUCKING WAREHOUSE PARTY.

00:12.280 --> 00:14.182
IT'S NOT EXACTLY
A PROMPT SITUATION.

00:14.282 --> 00:15.849
WHY ARE WE EVEN GOING?

00:15.949 --> 00:18.018
BECAUSE, MARNIE,
JADED AS I AM,

00:18.119 --> 00:22.323
I STILL HOLD OUT HOPE
THAT THE NEXT PARTY WILL BE
THE BEST PARTY EVER.

00:22.423 --> 00:24.525
OKAY, BEST PARTY EVER--
TO ME THAT'S LIKE SAYING

00:24.625 --> 00:27.361
- BEST GYM EVER OR BEST
NATURE DOCUMENTARY EVER.
- ( phone chimes )

00:27.461 --> 00:30.398
LIKE, HOW GOOD
CAN IT REALLY BE?

00:30.498 --> 00:32.165
THIS IS ODD.

00:32.266 --> 00:35.136
JUST GOT A TEXT MESSAGE.
"WHAT ARE YOU UP TO?"

00:35.236 --> 00:36.870
I DON'T KNOW THIS NUMBER.

00:36.970 --> 00:38.806
ASK WHO IT IS.

00:38.906 --> 00:40.941
NO.
THAT'S NO FUN.

00:41.041 --> 00:44.645
"AT BEST PARTY EVER."

00:44.745 --> 00:46.180
( laughs )

00:46.280 --> 00:49.617
"45 BUSHWICK PLACE.
COME."

00:49.717 --> 00:52.820
Marnie:
I THINK MAYBE
I FOUND IT.

00:52.920 --> 00:55.856
OKAY, LET'S GO.

00:55.956 --> 00:57.925
IT LOOKS
BIG AND SCARY.

00:58.025 --> 00:59.227
( music playing )

00:59.327 --> 01:01.662
THERE ARE A LOT
OF PEOPLE HERE.

01:01.762 --> 01:03.097
OF COURSE THERE ARE,

01:03.197 --> 01:04.897
BECAUSE EVERY SINGLE
PERSON IS COMING.

01:04.998 --> 01:07.168
I DON'T KNOW HOW TO PROPERLY
COMMUNICATE THIS TO YOU GUYS

01:07.268 --> 01:09.270
IF YOU HAVEN'T HEARD ME YET,
BUT ALL OF BROOKLYN

01:09.370 --> 01:11.905
AND TWO-THIRDS OF MANHATTAN
WILL BE HERE.

01:12.005 --> 01:14.542
OH, MY GOSH, I MEAN,
I JUST HOPE CHARLIE'S
OKAY SEEING ME.

01:14.642 --> 01:17.645
HIS BAND IS PLAYING.
I JUST CANNOT TAKE
A SCENE RIGHT NOW.

01:17.745 --> 01:19.980
YOU WOULD NEVER EVEN FIND HIM.
IT'S LIKE "WATERWORLD" IN THERE.

01:20.080 --> 01:21.982
IT DOESN'T MATTER.
IT DOESN'T MATTER.

01:22.082 --> 01:23.517
WE ARE HERE NOW.

01:23.617 --> 01:25.419
* And watch she gon'
get Donkey Kong *

01:25.519 --> 01:27.588
* Baby, if you're ready
for things to get heavy *

01:27.688 --> 01:29.457
* I get on the floor and act
a fool if you let me, dale *

01:29.557 --> 01:31.692
* Don't believe me,
just bet me *

01:31.792 --> 01:33.694
* My name ain't Keith,
but I see the way
you sweat me *

01:33.794 --> 01:35.329
* LA, Miami, New York

01:35.429 --> 01:37.097
* Say no more,
get on the floor *

01:37.198 --> 01:39.066
* La la la la la

01:39.167 --> 01:42.303
* La la la la la
la la la la... *

01:42.403 --> 01:46.106
JOIN THE MOVEMENT.
TITS OUT FOR CHRISTMAS.

01:47.641 --> 01:50.344
PROMISE ME WE'LL STICK
TOGETHER IN THERE, OKAY?

01:50.444 --> 01:52.480
WHAT AM I GONNA DO?
GO FIND MY FIXED-GEAR
BIKE-RIDING FRIENDS?

01:52.580 --> 01:54.482
- I'M A LOSER.
- YOU'RE ACTUALLY NOT.

01:54.582 --> 01:56.717
IT'S SOME WEIRD MYTHOLOGY
YOU HAVE ABOUT YOURSELF,

01:56.817 --> 02:00.120
KIND OF LIKE THE IDEA
THAT YOU NEED TO GET 11
HOURS OF SLEEP EVERY NIGHT.

02:00.221 --> 02:02.856
I DO EVER SINCE I HAD MONO.

02:08.127 --> 02:10.431
OH, MY GOD,
IS THAT SHOSHANNA?

02:10.531 --> 02:12.500
SHOSH!

02:13.834 --> 02:16.804
- SHOSHANNA!
- HI. HI.

02:16.904 --> 02:17.871
GET OVER HERE.

02:17.971 --> 02:19.773
SORRY.

02:19.873 --> 02:21.675
SORRY.
EXCUSE ME.

02:21.775 --> 02:24.178
OH, MY GOD.
THANK GOD.

02:24.278 --> 02:26.079
- OH, MY GOD.
- YOU LOOK REALLY SWEET.

02:26.180 --> 02:27.681
- REALLY? NO.
- YEAH.

02:27.781 --> 02:30.351
I MEAN, THIS IS LIKE
SIX MONTHS OLD,
THIS OUTFIT.

02:30.451 --> 02:32.953
UM, I'VE LITERALLY
BEEN HERE FOR TWO HOURS

02:33.053 --> 02:34.322
AND I HAVEN'T
SPOKEN TO ANYBODY.

02:34.422 --> 02:36.590
I'M SO HAPPY TO SEE YOU,
I COULD MURDER YOU.

02:36.690 --> 02:39.059
OH, MY GOD,
AND YOUR BOYFRIEND'S
BAND IS PLAYING.

02:39.159 --> 02:41.495
NOW I HAVE TO GO
SAY HI.

02:41.595 --> 02:44.532
- NO, YOU DON'T.
- YES, I DO.

02:46.300 --> 02:49.169
( band playing )

03:11.459 --> 03:13.761
- ( music ends )
- ( crowd cheering )

03:13.861 --> 03:15.563
THANK YOU.

03:15.663 --> 03:18.065
WHOEVER BROUGHT
A FUCKING BABY,

03:18.165 --> 03:20.000
YOU DON'T BRING A BABY
TO A PARTY LIKE THIS.

03:20.100 --> 03:22.135
USE YOUR FUCKING HEAD.

03:22.236 --> 03:24.104
WE'RE QUESTIONABLE GOODS,
FULLY DOWNLOADABLE

03:24.204 --> 03:26.374
AT QUESTIONABLEGOODS.TV.
HAVE A GOOD NIGHT.

03:26.474 --> 03:28.909
( crowd cheering )

03:37.251 --> 03:39.453
- OH.
- HEY.

03:39.553 --> 03:42.323
HEY.

03:42.423 --> 03:45.158
MM-MMM.
IT'S NICE TO SEE
YOUR FACE.

03:45.259 --> 03:49.463
YEAH, I THOUGHT
IT MIGHT BE.
NICE SET.

03:49.563 --> 03:50.764
THANK YOU.

03:50.864 --> 03:52.800
IT'S JUST NICE TO SEE
THAT YOU'RE PLAYING.

03:52.900 --> 03:55.235
YOU KNOW, I KNOW YOU
DIDN'T THINK YOU WERE
DOING THAT ENOUGH.

03:55.336 --> 03:58.472
YEAH, RIGHT. NO, ACTUALLY,
WE'VE GOT SOME REALLY
GREAT THINGS LINED UP.

03:58.572 --> 04:00.541
I'M REALLY, REALLY HAPPY
FOR YOU, CHARLIE.

04:00.641 --> 04:02.042
THANKS.

04:02.142 --> 04:04.578
I MEAN, ALL I EVER
WANTED FOR YOU WAS

04:04.678 --> 04:08.549
TO BE ABLE TO FIND
SATISFACTION OUTSIDE
OF OUR RELATIONSHIP.

04:09.149 --> 04:11.218
OH.

04:11.319 --> 04:13.321
UM, IT'S GOOD
TO SEE YOU.

04:13.421 --> 04:14.888
YEAH. YEAH.
NO, YOU, TOO.

04:14.988 --> 04:16.524
YOU LOOK GREAT.

04:16.624 --> 04:19.226
THIS FEELS VERY, LIKE,
CORDIAL AND GROWN-UP.

04:19.327 --> 04:21.228
YEAH.
YEAH, RIGHT?

04:21.329 --> 04:23.163
WELL, IT'S--

04:23.263 --> 04:25.265
YOU KNOW, IT'S MATURE.

04:25.366 --> 04:26.934
- YEAH.
- RIGHT?

04:27.034 --> 04:28.436
- AH!
- OOH!

04:28.536 --> 04:30.671
- YOU WERE...
- WHOA, WHOA.

04:30.771 --> 04:32.673
- ...FUCKING AWESOME.
- SHH, SHH.

04:32.773 --> 04:34.608
- THANK YOU.
- YOU WERE AMAZING.

04:34.708 --> 04:38.312
- UM, MARNIE,
THIS IS AUDREY.
- HI.

04:38.412 --> 04:40.213
HI. NICE TO MEET YOU.
HOW GOOD WAS HE?

04:40.314 --> 04:43.317
IT WAS YOUR FIRST GIG
IN, LIKE, FOREVER AND
YOU GUYS ROCKED IT.

04:43.417 --> 04:45.152
- HMM, GIG.
- I'M SO IMPRESSED.

04:45.252 --> 04:48.389
- UM, SORRY, WHAT IS--
WHAT IS GOING ON?
- ( loud music playing )

04:48.489 --> 04:49.623
- WHAT?
- ( crowd cheering )

04:49.723 --> 04:53.093
WHAT-- WHAT IS
GOING ON WITH THIS?

04:53.193 --> 04:55.629
I DON'T UNDERSTAND.

04:55.729 --> 04:59.400
- IT'S BEEN TWO WEEKS.
- UH, YEAH.

04:59.500 --> 05:01.268
THIS HAPPENED
IN TWO WEEKS?

05:01.369 --> 05:03.371
UH, YEAH.

05:03.471 --> 05:06.039
NO, I GUESS.
WE-- WE JUST MET

05:06.139 --> 05:08.442
AND SORT OF CLICKED.

05:10.210 --> 05:11.178
I'M SORRY,
WHO ARE YOU?

05:11.278 --> 05:13.313
YOU'VE NEVER HEARD
OF ME?

05:13.414 --> 05:15.215
NO, SHOULD I HAVE?

05:15.315 --> 05:17.851
ARE YOU ONE OF THOSE
"REAL HOUSEWIVES"?

05:17.951 --> 05:19.987
OH.

05:20.087 --> 05:22.990
YOU ARE A SOCIOPATH.

05:25.926 --> 05:28.095
( music playing )

05:29.663 --> 05:32.866
- THIS ROOM
IS AMATEUR HOUR.
- TOTALLY.

05:32.966 --> 05:36.003
ALTHOUGH I DO LOVE A MAN
WHO ONLY HANGS OUT WITH DYKES.

05:36.103 --> 05:37.705
LOOK AT THEM.

05:37.805 --> 05:40.340
THEY'RE FAWNING ALL OVER HIM
LIKE HE OWNS A HOME DEPOT.

05:40.441 --> 05:42.242
WHOO-HOO-HOO!

05:42.342 --> 05:44.678
WHOO!
ALL RIGHT!

05:46.079 --> 05:47.448
OKAY, THAT'S ADAM.

05:47.548 --> 05:50.350
HE DOES SORT OF LOOK
LIKE THE ORIGINAL MAN.

05:50.451 --> 05:53.086
NO, LIKE MY ADAM.
LIKE ADAM ADAM.

05:55.355 --> 05:57.791
I'VE NEVER SEEN HIM
OUTSIDE HIS HOUSE.

05:57.891 --> 05:59.960
I'VE NEVER SEEN
HIM WITH A SHIRT ON.

06:00.060 --> 06:02.362
THE LAST TIME
I TALKED TO HIM,
HE SAID THAT HE MISSED ME

06:02.463 --> 06:03.964
AND HE WOULD PAY ME TO COME
EAT POPCORN WITH HIM,

06:04.064 --> 06:06.834
BUT THEN HE HASN'T
RETURNED A TEXT OF MINE
IN OVER TWO WEEKS.

06:06.934 --> 06:09.737
AND I WAS JUST COMING TO TERMS
WITH THE IDEA THAT HE WAS DEAD.

06:09.837 --> 06:11.539
WHY ARE YOU ALL
STANDING IN A LINE?

06:11.639 --> 06:15.008
BECAUSE THAT IS ADAM
AND I AM NOT GONNA
TALK TO HIM.

06:16.510 --> 06:18.846
WELL, I JUST WATCHED
CHARLIE GET CLIMBED

06:18.946 --> 06:21.449
LIKE A GYM CLASS ROPE
BY A TINY NAVAJO.

06:21.549 --> 06:23.984
AND HE DIDN'T STOP HER
BECAUSE HE HAS A GIRLFRIEND

06:24.084 --> 06:25.686
AND SHE IS HIS GIRLFRIEND.

06:25.786 --> 06:28.656
WHAT THE FUCK
IS SHE DOING?

06:30.524 --> 06:33.627
( shouting )

06:36.029 --> 06:38.499
OH, HANNAH?
HANNAH!

06:38.599 --> 06:40.834
HEY, GUYS,
THAT'S HANNAH.

06:40.934 --> 06:42.903
- Woman: HANNAH?
- Adam: HANNAH!

06:43.003 --> 06:45.372
TELL HER TO COME BACK.

06:45.473 --> 06:48.676
- YOU FUCKING SCARED HER!
- OH, NO! NO, NO!

06:48.776 --> 06:51.579
* Godzilla bankroll,
stones from Sierra Leone *

06:51.679 --> 06:54.047
* Yo, I ain't got it all,
that means I'm barely home *

06:54.147 --> 06:56.917
* Trailblazers stay ballin',
revenge is my arts... *

06:57.017 --> 06:58.385
YOU LOOK INCREDIBLE.

06:58.486 --> 07:00.854
SO DOES EVERYONE
IN THE "AGE OF INNOCENCE"
FAN CLUB

07:00.954 --> 07:02.856
GET ONE OF THESE
OR JUST THE GOLD MEMBERS?

07:02.956 --> 07:05.826
- EVERYONE.
- EVERYONE GETS ONE?

07:05.926 --> 07:08.095
- IT'S LIKE
WEARABLE TAXIDERMY.
- MMM.

07:08.195 --> 07:11.031
LOOKS LIKE IT'S JUST READY
TO LIKE JUST MOUTH-FUCK YOU.

07:11.131 --> 07:14.234
- JUST FUCKING--
- HOW'S YOUR BUG-EYED
GIRLFRIEND?

07:14.334 --> 07:15.603
SHE'S NOT
MY GIRLFRIEND ANYMORE.

07:15.703 --> 07:17.270
- NO?
- MM-MM, DIDN'T WORK.

07:17.370 --> 07:19.106
- WHY?
- EH, A BUNCH OF REASONS.

07:19.206 --> 07:21.509
HER FATHER'S A SHRINK.
SHE LAUGHS AT HER OWN JOKES.

07:21.609 --> 07:23.076
SO SEXUAL--

07:23.176 --> 07:24.878
- HI. HI. HI.
- HI.

07:24.978 --> 07:26.947
I'VE BEEN LOOKING FOR YOU.
I JUST HAD THIS CRAZY
REALIZATION.

07:27.047 --> 07:29.149
IT'S KIND OF AMAZING
AND I'M GONNA SHARE IT
WITH YOU RIGHT NOW, OKAY?

07:29.249 --> 07:31.952
OKAY, SO I WAS THINKING--
NO, I FEEL, I BELIEVE

07:32.052 --> 07:34.054
THAT I CAN BE MUCH MORE
AWESOME IN KICKBOXING CLASS.

07:34.154 --> 07:36.857
MAYBE I CAN EVEN
MOVE TOWARDS THE FRONT
AND PEOPLE WOULD FOLLOW ME.

07:36.957 --> 07:39.527
- WHO THE FUCK IS THIS?
- THIS IS MY COUSIN SHOSHANNA.

07:39.627 --> 07:41.595
SHOSHANNA, RAY.
RAY, SHOSHANNA.

07:41.695 --> 07:43.330
- SHE IS MY MATERNAL COUSIN.
- HI. NICE TO MEET YOU.

07:43.430 --> 07:46.534
SO, LIKE, WHAT IS IT
ABOUT WOMEN THAT MAKES
CERTAIN PEOPLE

07:46.634 --> 07:50.070
MOVE TOWARDS THE FRONT, LIKE,
BECAUSE THEY HAVE A BRAZILIAN
BLOWOUT OR THEY'RE ENGAGED?

07:50.170 --> 07:52.906
NO, THOSE ARE MATERIAL
CONCERNS THAT MAKE THEM
FEEL THE CONFIDENCE

07:53.006 --> 07:54.542
TO MOVE TOWARDS THE FRONT,
BUT IT'S NOT REAL.

07:54.642 --> 07:56.243
THERE ARE ALWAYS TWO SPACES
AT LEAST NEAR THE FRONT,

07:56.343 --> 07:58.045
AND I WORK HARD
AND I KICK ASS

07:58.145 --> 08:00.113
AND I'M GOING
TOWARDS THE FRONT.
IS IT SO CRAZY HOT IN HERE?

08:00.213 --> 08:03.183
- ARE YOU--
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?
- MM-HMM, I THINK SO.

08:03.283 --> 08:05.052
I JUST-- I'M REALLY,
REALLY HIGH.

08:05.152 --> 08:06.453
I'M LIKE OUT-OF-MY-MIND HIGH.

08:06.554 --> 08:08.288
I SMOKED SOME POT IN LINE
FOR THE BATHROOM,

08:08.388 --> 08:10.958
WHICH IS SO DIRTY.
DO NOT GO IN THERE
UNLESS IT'S AN EMERGE.

08:11.058 --> 08:13.727
WITH THESE GUYS
IN LINE FOR THE BATHROOM,
THEY GAVE ME SOME POT

08:13.827 --> 08:16.396
OUT OF A PIPE,
BUT IT WAS A STEM.
THEY KEPT CALLING IT A STEM.

08:16.496 --> 08:19.166
- IT WAS A STEM.
- I DON'T THINK SHE'S HIGH
ON MARIJUANA.

08:19.266 --> 08:20.968
- WAS IT A CRACK STEM?
- NO.

08:21.068 --> 08:22.736
- DID YOU SMOKE CRACK?
- NO.

08:22.836 --> 08:25.005
- LITTLE WHITE ROCKS?
- NO!

08:25.105 --> 08:28.976
IT WAS A GLASS CIGARETTE
AND I'M HIGH.

08:29.076 --> 08:31.712
AND MY EARS FEEL LIKE POPPING.
DO YOUR EARS FEEL LIKE POPPING?

08:31.812 --> 08:35.883
OKAY, HEY, LOOK AT ME.
YOU SMOKED CRACK.

08:35.982 --> 08:39.587
YOU SMOKED
JUST SOME CRACK.

08:39.687 --> 08:41.554
OH, MY GOD,
DON'T TELL MY MOM.

08:41.655 --> 08:42.990
DON'T EVEN TELL ME.

08:43.090 --> 08:45.292
I MATRICULATE AT N.Y.U.
AND I JUST SMOKED CRACK.

08:45.392 --> 08:47.661
- WHAT'S GOING TO HAPPEN?
- YOU'RE GONNA BE FINE, OKAY?

08:47.761 --> 08:51.264
CRACK CAN BE REALLY FUN
UNDER THE RIGHT CIRCUMSTANCES

08:51.364 --> 08:53.133
AND IT ONLY LASTS
A LITTLE WHILE.

08:53.233 --> 08:56.770
AND I'LL TAKE CARE OF YOU.
I WILL BE YOUR CRACK
SPIRIT GUIDE.

08:56.870 --> 08:59.372
OKAY?

08:59.472 --> 09:02.910
SHH, SHH.

09:04.077 --> 09:05.412
OH, MY GOD.

09:05.512 --> 09:07.848
- OH, MY FUCKING GOD.
- WHAT? WHAT IS IT?

09:10.951 --> 09:13.353
CAN YOU WATCH HER
FOR ONE SECOND?

09:13.453 --> 09:15.255
HER? ARE YOU
FUCKING KIDDING ME?
NO WAY.

09:15.355 --> 09:17.825
I'M NOT
A FUCKING JAP DAY CARE.
ABSOLUTELY NOT.

09:17.925 --> 09:19.593
PLEASE.
THAT'S MY BOSS
RIGHT THERE.

09:19.693 --> 09:22.329
ALL I'M ASKING IS THAT
YOU JUST MAKE SURE

09:22.429 --> 09:26.233
SHE DOESN'T JUMP OFF
A ROOF OR GET FINGERED
BY A BEAT-BOXER.

09:26.333 --> 09:29.870
OKAY? HEY, SHOSH,
THIS IS RAY.
REMEMBER RAY?

09:29.970 --> 09:31.939
HE'S GONNA BE YOUR
NEW CRACK SPIRIT GUIDE.

09:32.039 --> 09:34.642
OKAY, I WILL BE BACK.
I'LL BE RIGHT BACK.

09:36.877 --> 09:38.879
SO HOW LONG--
HEY.

09:38.979 --> 09:41.048
HEY! HEY!
HEY, COME BACK!

09:41.148 --> 09:44.484
WAIT! OVER THERE--
WHERE ARE YOU GOING?
HEY!

09:44.584 --> 09:46.586
IT'S BEEN TWO WEEKS.
YOU KNOW WHAT I MEAN?

09:46.687 --> 09:48.822
LIKE...

09:50.991 --> 09:53.794
WHAT IF-- I HAVEN'T DONE
ANYTHING IN TWO WEEKS.

09:56.129 --> 09:58.331
I GOT YOUR TEXT.

09:58.431 --> 10:00.400
OH, YOU--
OH, YEAH.

10:00.500 --> 10:02.102
- YEAH.
- YEAH.

10:02.202 --> 10:05.238
THIS IS A KILLER PARTY.
LIKING THE VIBE.

10:05.338 --> 10:07.007
- IS THAT SO?
- YEAH.

10:07.107 --> 10:08.642
- LIKING THE VIBE?
- GOOD VIBE.

10:08.742 --> 10:10.110
OH, SORRY.
I'M SORRY.

10:10.210 --> 10:12.212
YOU'RE GONNA GO TO THE FRONT
IN KICKBOXING CLASS.

10:12.312 --> 10:14.147
- IT'S OKAY. IT'S OKAY.
- Ray: SHOSHANNA!

10:14.247 --> 10:15.949
JUST DO NOT GET RAPED
BY THE MAN IN PLAID.

10:16.049 --> 10:18.018
DON'T GET RAPED
BY THE MAN IN PLAID.

10:18.118 --> 10:20.888
I'M YOUR CRACK
SPIRIT GUIDE!

10:20.988 --> 10:22.790
STOP!

10:46.313 --> 10:49.182
OH, THANKS,
BUT NO, THANKS.

10:49.282 --> 10:51.952
I PROBABLY SHOULDN'T.
I DON'T DRINK WELL.

10:53.520 --> 10:55.455
YOU'RE HANNAH, RIGHT?

10:55.555 --> 10:57.624
I AM, YEAH.
YOU'RE FRIENDS WITH ADAM?

10:57.725 --> 10:59.592
YEAH. TAKO.

10:59.693 --> 11:01.294
IT'S NICE
TO MEET YOU, TAKO.

11:01.394 --> 11:03.596
YEAH.
IT'S WITH A "K."

11:03.697 --> 11:05.465
OH, OKAY.
SO HOW DO YOU PRONOUNCE IT?

11:05.565 --> 11:07.334
LIKE THAT.
YOU GOT IT.

11:07.434 --> 11:10.337
IT'S JUST I CAN USUALLY
TELL WHEN SOMEONE THINKS
IT'S WITH A "C."

11:10.437 --> 11:12.940
ALL RIGHT, WELL,
NEVER AGAIN.

11:13.040 --> 11:14.607
IT'S NOT THAT BIG A DEAL.

11:14.708 --> 11:16.676
IT'S JUST SOMETHING
THAT'S IMPORTANT TO ME.

11:16.777 --> 11:18.278
YEAH, OF COURSE.
I TOTALLY UNDERSTAND.

11:18.378 --> 11:20.180
SOMETIMES PEOPLE
PRONOUNCE MY NAME "HANA"

11:20.280 --> 11:23.550
LIKE I'M ISRAELI
OR SOMETHING AND IT CAN BE
COMPLETELY DISORIENTING.

11:23.650 --> 11:25.218
YEAH, I KNOW, RIGHT?

11:25.318 --> 11:27.354
HEY, ARE YOU SURE
YOU DON'T WANT A DRINK?

11:27.454 --> 11:28.789
I'M GOOD, YEAH.
I SHOULDN'T.

11:28.889 --> 11:30.590
IT NEVER GOES WELL
FOR ME.

11:30.690 --> 11:32.425
LAST TIME I GOT DRUNK,
I ATE ALL THIS BRIE

11:32.525 --> 11:34.027
AND I THREW UP
ON MY CELL PHONE.

11:34.127 --> 11:36.429
OKAY, AWESOME.

11:36.529 --> 11:40.033
ALL RIGHT,
NO ALCOHOL FOR YOU.

11:41.068 --> 11:43.904
MMM, OH.

11:44.004 --> 11:45.773
IS THAT HOW
YOU KNOW ADAM?

11:45.873 --> 11:48.441
- HOW?
- THROUGH A.A.

11:48.541 --> 11:52.312
OH, NO.
HE'S IN A.A.?

11:54.147 --> 11:56.049
OH, SHIT.

11:56.149 --> 11:57.751
I JUST BLEW
HIS ANONYMOUSNESS.

11:57.851 --> 12:00.020
OH, BALLS, MAN.

12:00.120 --> 12:01.688
DON'T TELL HIM,
ALL RIGHT?

12:01.789 --> 12:04.191
I JUST ASSUMED THAT
EVERYONE THAT KNEW HIM,

12:04.291 --> 12:07.594
LIKE, I MEAN, REALLY
KNEW HIM, KNEW THAT.

