YOU TWO ARE CUT
FROM THE SAME CLOTH,
AREN'T YOU?

20:04.704 --> 20:06.105
WHAT?

20:06.205 --> 20:08.074
I HAVEN'T SEEN YOU
SINCE COLLEGE,

20:08.174 --> 20:10.877
