22:03.790 --> 22:07.494
THAT I FOLLOWED YOU
TO BUSHWICK AND GOT
BEAT UP BY CRUSTY PUNKS?

22:09.095 --> 22:11.398
THAT WAS CLEARLY
YOUR FIRST FIGHT.

22:11.498 --> 22:14.000
YOU'RE LUCKY IT
WASN'T YOUR LAST.

22:14.100 --> 22:17.336
