25:29.428 --> 25:31.798
AND YOUR SICK
INSTINCTS, OKAY?

25:31.898 --> 25:34.834
AND I'M NOT SCARED TO BE
VERY CLEAR WITH PEOPLE

25:34.934 --> 25:37.837
ABOUT THE KIND OF MAN
THAT YOU ARE.

25:37.937 --> 25:39.939
I AM SO FUCKING
OUT OF HERE.

25:40.039 --> 25:42.942
OH, THAT'S A REAL CHANGE.
